{
  "schema": 1,
  "id": "studio",
  "name": {
    "en": "Studio",
    "zh": "一般棚燈"
  },
  "desc": {
    "en": "The standard three-point setup. The key lights the subject, the fill lifts the shadows, and the rim separates the character from the background.",
    "zh": "標準的主光、輔光、輪廓光三點打光。主光的目的為照亮、輔光的目的為提亮暗部、輪廓光則能夠把角色從背景裡凸顯出來。"
  },
  "tip": {
    "en": "Keep a clear hierarchy between light and dark. The key must be brighter than the fill — a scene needs both to have depth.",
    "zh": "打光要維持亮暗的主次感，主光一定要比輔光亮，有亮有暗場景才會有層次與立體感。"
  },
